review.reviewBody:
Ghati Paneer (GF) is an outstanding curry. The spice mix and medium-hot is just amazing with the soft paneer cubes. 

Pairs really well with fresh Garlic Naan or Basmati rice. 

Highly recommend
So fresh and delicious, this restaurant in the neighbourhood is a gem! Vindaloo curry, biryani and samosas were my favourite. Must try!!! Highly recommend.
Overall was a good meal but the Butter Chicken was a bit dry.

The consistency of the curry was too thin and runny and the chicken was very dry inside. The potion of rice was small for the price and not proportionate to the quantity of curry. Not a great experience.
